import { Table, TableHead, TableBody, TableRow, TableCell, Typography, } from "@mui/material"; const DTable = ({ data, title, totalLost }) => { return ( <> {title} Stage Came to Stage Lost/Disqualified from stage Moved to next stage Win Rate % {data.map((row) => ( {row.stage} {row.cameToStage.toFixed(0).toLocaleString()} {row.stage === "Won" ? "-" : row.lost.toLocaleString()} {row.stage === "Won" ? "-" : row.moved.toLocaleString()} {row.winRate} ))} Total - {totalLost.toLocaleString()} - -
); }; export default DTable;
